在化学中，'''硒酮'''是[[酮|酮]] 中的 [[氧|氧]] 原子被[[硒|硒]]取代而成的化合物。  硒-77 是一种[[硒的同位素|硒]] 的[[稳定同位素|稳定同位素]] ，因此可以通过[[核磁共振波谱|核磁共振波谱]]（NMR）分析含硒酮的化学物质。 硒酮可用作<sup>77</sup>Se-NMR的{{le|手性衍生剂|Chiral derivatizing agent}}。 <ref>{{cite journal |author1=J. Peng |author2=J. D. Odom |author3=R. B. Dunlap |author4=L. A. Silks III  |name-list-style=amp | title = Use of a selone chiral derivatizing agent for the absolute configurational assignment of stereogenic center | journal = Tetrahedron: Asymmetry | year=1994 | volume=5 | issue=9 | pages = 1627–1630 | doi = 10.1016/0957-4166(94)80066-9 |url=https://zenodo.org/record/1258653 }}</ref> 手性恶唑烷硒酮可用于{{le|恶唑烷酮 |Oxazolidinone}}的[[羟醛反应#埃文斯𫫇唑烷酮化学|埃文斯羟醛反应]]，可允许用<sup>77</sup>Se-NMR确定醛醇产物的[[对映体过量百分数|对映体过量百分数]]。 <ref>{{cite journal |author1=L. Silks |author2=D. Kimball |author3=D. Hatch | title = Chiral ''N''-Acetyl Selone-Promoted Aldol Reactions | journal = Synthetic Communications | year = 2009 | volume = 39 | issue = 4 | pages = 641–653 | doi = 10.1080/00397910802419706|s2cid=96583069 |display-authors=etal| url = https://zenodo.org/record/1234399 }}</ref>

与具有早期[[氧族元素|氧族元素]]的类似结构相反，硒酮具有更大的空间和电子稳定性。 <ref name=Oka>{{Cite journal| pages = 625–630| issue = 9| year = 2000| pmid = 10995200 | doi = 10.1021/ar980073b| volume = 33| journal = Accounts of Chemical Research| last1 = Okazaki | first1 = R.| last2 = Tokitoh | first2 = N.| title = Heavy ketones, the heavier element congeners of a ketone}}</ref> 硒代二苯基甲酮可以可逆地二聚。它已知在类似于[[Diels-Alder反应|Diels-Alder反应]]的反应中与1,3-环戊二烯进行环加成。 <ref>{{Cite journal| last1 = Erker | first1 = G.| last2 = Hock| last3 = Krüger| last4 = Werner| last5 = Klärner| last6 = Artschwager-Perl| title = Synthesis and Cycloadditions of Monomeric Selenobenzophenone| journal = Angewandte Chemie International Edition in English| volume = 29| issue = 9| pages = 1067| year = 1990 | doi = 10.1002/anie.199010671 | first2 = R. | first3 = C. | first4 = S. | first5 = F. G. | first6 = U.}}</ref>

